@database "IntuiNews.guide"

@Node Main "IntuiNews Documentation"

	@{u}IntuiNews 1.0@{uu}

A Mail- and Newsreader for the Universal Message System.

  Sorry, but there was not enough time to complete this english
documentation. We really hope to get it completed in the next few days and
then we will release a new complete archive.

  IntuiNews is really easy to use and you should understand it even
without any documentation. Take a look at the description of the
UMS-configuration-variables in the german documentation. We think the
examples are easy to understand and you will be able to do at least the
basic configuration.

@EndNode

